name: The Fenwick Dining Table - Davidson
description:
The Fenwick is a luxurious round dining table that is the ideal choice for those looking for maximum leg room and comfort.
Made by the skilled hands of British craftsmen, the table is available in any of DAVIDSON's luxurious finishes. The stunning radial pattern draws the eye, promising an outstanding level of craftsmanship.
The slimline, circular table top and sleek, central pedestal make the Fenwick a more lightweight option compared to some of the other designs in the collection, all standing on a smooth facetted base. The table features a luxurious gleaming collar in brass or nickel to the base for an extra touch of opulence.
